hanges to `cursor-default`."],[559,"By default, Hummingbird includes the `default` theme. To use a different prebuilt theme, simply import the corresponding CSS file in the main CSS file (e.g., `globals.css`). Each theme has built-in dark mode support, so dark mode will automatically work when the theme is imported."],[524,"By default, inline code elements (`<code>`) are styled with a specific text color and font size. When a `<code>` element is nested inside an `<a>` tag, it inherits the link's text color and font size."],[528,"By default, table captions (`<caption>`) are aligned to the left and positioned at the bottom of the table. They also have specific font weight and padding."],[522,"By default, unordered lists (`<ul>`) use disc bullets, and ordered lists (`<ol>`) use decimal numbers. Both types of lists have a left padding of `2rem` and a bottom margin of `1rem`. Nested lists have no bottom margin."],[359,"Caption"],[511,"Captions"],[126,"Card"],[135,"Card"],[133,"Card group"],[136,"CardImage"],[179,"Centered"],[657,"Checkbox"],[666,"Checkbox"],[308,"Circle"],[132,"Clickable"],[147,"Close Button"],[154,"CloseButton"],[507,"Code"],[630,"Col"],[162,"Collapsible"],[175,"Collapsible is a behavior-only primitive and ships no Hummingbird classes of its own. The panel's height is animated through `data-state`; the trigger and content take any Hummingbird utility classes as needed."],[422,"Color palettes"],[575,"Color utilities like `bg-primary-light`, `text-primary-dark`, and many\nmore"],[19,"Colors"],[56,"Colors"],[108,"Colors"],[257,"Colors"],[310,"Colors"],[355,"Colors"],[387,"Colors"],[416,"Colors"],[660,"Colors"],[694,"Colors"],[721,"Colors"],[751,"Colors"],[771,"Colors"],[787,"Colors"],[616,"Columns"],[642,"Columns can be modified with options for alignment, ordering, and offsetting using the flexbox grid system."],[450,"Component Customization"],[628,"Container"],[579,"Container query variants like `@sm:*` and size utilities like `max-w-md`"],[441,"Contrast